HEADWORD: Icy
<hw>I"cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <amorph>[<pos>Compar.</pos>
<adjf>Icier</adjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>superl.</pos>
<adjf>Iciest</adjf>.]</amorph> <ety>[AS. <ets>⟦imac⟧sig</ets>. See
<er>Ice</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Pertaining to, resembling, or
abounding in, ice; cold; frosty.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Icy</xex>
chains.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Shak.</au> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Icy</xex> region.⟦rdquo⟧
